text: Ivan Bulajić (Serbian Cyrillic: Иван Булајић; born 29 March 1995) is a Serbian football goalkeeper who plays for Radnički Niš II. ==Club career== On 27 June 2018, Bulajić signed with Radnički Niš.FK Radnički: Novi igrači u klubu sa Čaira at naissus.info 27 June 2018. Bulajić made his official debut for Radnički Niš in 3 fixture match of the 2018–19 Serbian SuperLiga season against Dinamo Vranje, played on 5 August 2018, replacing Mladen Živković in 34 minute after injury.RADNIČKI NIŠ VS.
